- handlers/admin.py: full admin panel guarded by ADMIN_IDS env list
- broadcast iterates all users and reports sent/failed counts
- set_tier overrides user tier without web round-trip
- ban/unban add a 'banned' boolean column lazily via _ensure_banned_column
- stats_global aggregates deposits, wins/losses, winrate across linked accounts
- main.py: register admin router first
